    Hello,<br>
    <br>
    ddccontrol told me to send its output to this e-mail addess.<br>
    So, here I am :-)<br>
    <br>
    I try to control the brightness of an Evervision VGG128012-5TSLWB.
    To some extend it seems that a I2C-device is assigned to this
    monitor. However, there is no monitor description XML available.<br>
    <br>
    In its output <tt>ddccontrol</tt> states "<tt>DDC/CI supported: No"</tt><br>
    Is this because of the missing XML file or is that a result of
    probing the found i2c device?<br>
    <br>
    Maybe the information below could help you in your assessment.<br>
    <br>
    <br>
    Thank you and best regards,<br>
    Daniel Huber<br>
